{"name":"Young Remorhaz","size":"large","type":"Monstrosity","tag":"","alignment":"unaligned","hitDice":"10","armorName":"natural armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":3,"otherArmorDesc":"17 (natural armor)","speed":"40","burrowSpeed":"25","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"85 (10d10 + 30)","speedDesc":"30 ft., burrow 20 ft.","strPoints":"18","dexPoints":"13","conPoints":"17","intPoints":"3","wisPoints":"10","chaPoints":"4","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"60","tremorsense":"60","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"4","customCr":"11 (7,200 XP)","customProf":4,"isLegendary":true,"legendariesDescription":"The [MON] can take one legendary action at the end of another creature's turn. The [MON] regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the remorhaz can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the remorhaz can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The remorhaz can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the remorhaz's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the remorhaz's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the remorhaz dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Heated Body","desc":"A creature that touches the [MON] or hits it with a melee attack while within 5 feet of it takes [1d8] fire damage."}],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"The [MON] makes two attacks, one trample and one bite."},{"name":"Bite","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 10 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [STR 3d8] piercing damage plus [1d8] fire damage. If the target is a creature, it is grappled (escape DC [STR SAVE]). Until this grapple ends, the target is restrained, and the [MON] can't bite another target."},{"name":"Trample","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack_: [STR ATCK] to hit, 5ft., one target. _Hit_ [STR 1d8] bludgeoning plus [1d8] fire damage. The target must make a DC [STR SAVE] strength saving throw or be knocked prone."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[{"name":"Round 1: Burrow","desc":"The [MON] moves its burrow speed."},{"name":"Round 2: Drag Beneath","desc":"The [MON] erupts from beneath a creature and makes a bite attack, then moves its burrow speed underground."}],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[],"skills":[],"damagetypes":[{"name":"cold","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"},{"name":"fire","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"}],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"remorhaz","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":false,"separationPoint":1,"damage":[]}